bilingual.target: 这种病会导致身体的无规律。

bilingual.source: She felt physical pain after the accident.
bilingual.target: 她在事故后感到身体的疼痛。
医生进行了身体的检查。

bilingual.source: Physical therapy helped him recover from the injury.
bilingual.target: 身体的治疗帮助他从伤病中恢复。

bilingual.source: He enjoys physical activities like hiking and swimming.
bilingual.target: 他喜欢徒步旅行和游泳等身体的活动。

bilingual.source: Regular exercise is important for maintaining physical health.
bilingual.target: 定期锻炼对保持身体的健康很重要。

bilingual.source: Yoga can be a spiritual practice as well as a physical one.
bilingual.target: 瑜伽既可以是心灵的练习，也可以是身体的练习。

bilingual.source: Kung fu is not just physical training, but also a mental discipline.
bilingual.target: 武功不仅仅是身体的训练，更是心灵的修炼。

bilingual.source: Self-defense is not just about physical skills but also mental preparation.
bilingual.target: 防身术不仅仅是关于身体的技能，还有心理的准备。

bilingual.source: Like physical fights, verbal fights can leave both sides bloodied.
bilingual.target: 和身体的对抗一样，口头打仗也会伤到双方。

list.abstract: physical（英[ˈfɪzɪkl]，美[ˈfɪzɪkl]），英语单词，作形容词时，有身体的、物质的、自然规律的等意思，作名词时，意思为体格检查以及现货股票。短语搭配有“physical activity”。例句有“Having regular physical and mental checkups”。 physical的词根为“phys-”，表示自然，自然科学，生长。词缀为“-ical”，表示“...的”。 physical edcution的意思为体育教育。歌手Dua Lipa有首复古单曲，名为《Physical》。
《Physical》是奥莉维亚·纽顿-约翰的单曲。

yingyinNormal.en: Army physical is that way. This is for giving blood.
yingyinNormal.zh: 部队体检在那边，这里是献血。

yingyinNormal.en: I made a physical change to match the spiritual one.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我改变了一下外在好配得上我的内在。

yingyinNormal.en: She's got some physical discomfort. Put in a request for a full physical at her next rotation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她有一些肢体不适，要求在她下次轮换时，做详细的肢体检查。

yingyinNormal.en: Each of us has a code for our optimal physical condition.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们每个人都有自己身体最佳状况的遗传密码。

yingyinNormal.en: On a scale of 1 to 10, how would you rate your pain? Physical, or emotional?
yingyinNormal.zh: 从一到十级，你的疼痛指数是？你是说生理上的，还是心理上的？

yingyinNormal.en: Today's the day Carol and I first consummated our physical relationship. Sex.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今天是我和卡萝第一次进行肉体接触，做爱。

yingyinNormal.en: Phonebooks. I was in charge of overseeing the printing of the physical phonebook.
yingyinNormal.zh: 电话簿，我是管审查纸质电话本的印刷的。

yingyinNormal.en: Still hurts. I seen no evidence of physical injury. It's a different kind of hurt.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但还是很痛。我没有检测出伤口。那是另外一种伤痛。

yingyinNormal.en: I gotta tell you if this were me, this guy would be in some serious physical danger.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果是我，他就等着挨揍吧。

yingyinNormal.en: What if he needs to... No, don't worry. You're not here for any of the physical stuff.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果他需要... 别担心，你不用做身体护理。

yingyinNormal.en: Sheldon, being physical with Amy is a huge step for you. Yeah, are you ready for this?
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢尔顿，跟艾米发生肉体关系可是重大的一步啊。是啊。你准备好了吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Now what are you doing? Other treatments include compassion, and physical reassurance.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你现在在做什么？其他治疗方法包括，关怀和安抚。

yingyinNormal.en: My quest has taken me through the physical, the metaphysical, the delusional and back.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的追求带领我穿过了物理，形而上学，幻觉又带了回来。

yingyinNormal.en: You can't know that. Course I can. There wasn't anything physical going on, was there?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你怎么可能知道？当然可能。你们之间没有身体接触了，对不对？

yingyinNormal.en: Imagine my attitude regarding prolonged physical proximity to Amy Farrah Fowler. Got it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你就可以想象得到我对与艾米·菲拉·福勒长时间身体接触的态度了。明白了。

yingyinNormal.en: Here's my question: it's the second date, you think she'll be expecting things to get physical?
yingyinNormal.zh: 问题就是，这是第二次约会，你觉得她会想要进一步的身体接触么？

yingyinNormal.en: So, Patrick, Louisa tells me you're a personal trainer. Life coaching, physical training, motivation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 帕特里克，路易莎跟我说你是私人健身教练。生活教练，健身教练，日常激励。

yingyinNormal.en: The first is physical. Push your bodies to the breaking point and you'll master the methods of combat.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第一阶段是体能训练，将你们的身体练到极限，掌握所有的格斗技巧。

yingyinNormal.en: Our job today is to analyze your needs, both psychological and physical. Sounds pretty straight forward.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今天的任务是分析你的需求心理以及身体两个层面的。直接了当。

yingyinNormal.en: You see, when a female witnesses an exhibition of physical domination, she produces the hormone oxytocin.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你知道吗，当女性看到你在展示力量时她会产生荷尔蒙催产素。

examination_example.sentence: Big chains have been collecting sales tax nationwide because they typically have <highlight>physical</highlight> stores in whatever state a purchase is being shipped to.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 大型连锁企业一直在全国范围内征收销售税，因为它们通常在货物运输到的任何州都有实体店。

examination_example.sentence: You could limit distractions by reading only <highlight>physical</highlight> books, or on single-purpose e-readers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你可以通过只读实体书或使用单一用途的电子阅读器来减少分心。

examination_example.sentence: Hence it is metaphysical; but the means of expression is purely and exclusively <highlight>physical</highlight>: sound.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 因此，音乐是形而上学的；但音乐的表达方式却纯粹只有一种有形的形态——声音。

sense_info_list.en: relating to the body as opposed to the mind

examination_example.sentence: Like <highlight>physical</highlight> fights, verbal fights can leave both sides bloodied.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 和肢体冲突一样，言语冲突也会让双方流血。

examination_example.sentence: The bargain is very pure: Employee puts in hours of <highlight>physical</highlight> or mental labor and employee draws out life-sustaining moola.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这种交易非常纯粹：员工投入时间从事体力或脑力劳动，获取维持生计的收入。

examination_example.sentence: Write a letter of about 100 words to the president of your university, suggesting how to improve students' <highlight>physical</highlight> condition.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 给你的大学校长写一封100字左右的信，给出如何改善学生的身体状况的建议。

sense_info_list.en: relating to physics or the operation of natural forces generally

examination_example.sentence: Ten minutes of activity per day is a good start, says Marcus Jackovitz, DPT, a <highlight>physical</highlight> therapist at the University of Miami Hospital.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 迈阿密大学医院物理治疗师、发展治疗学的Marcus Jackovitz说，每天活动10分钟是一个好的开始。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

sense_info_list.en: relating to the body as opposed to the mind

examination_example.sentence: They were often forced to work at hard <highlight>physical</highlight> jobs for little money.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们经常被迫从事艰苦的体力劳动，却挣不到多少钱。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Physical</highlight> problems are another factor that can cause students to fall asleep in class.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 身体问题是另一个可能导致学生在课堂上打瞌睡的原因。

examination_example.sentence: Doing a lot of <highlight>physical</highlight> activities and having a healthy diet will help have normal body weight.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 多做身体锻炼和保持健康饮食有助于保持正常的体重。

sense_info_list.en: a medical examination to determine a person's bodily fitness

examination_example.sentence: a <highlight>physical</highlight> exam
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一次体检

examination_example.sentence: I wonder how often the students have a <highlight>physical</highlight> examination.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我想知道学生们多久体检一次。

sense_info_list.en: relating to things perceived through the senses as opposed to the mind

examination_example.sentence: More surprisingly, it's young people who are buying the most <highlight>physical</highlight> books.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 更令人惊讶的是，买实体书最多的是年轻人。
